sc_cat_item.description:
Apple's iPhone 8 isn't just bigger—it's better in every way. A 4.7-inch Retina HD display. An A11 Bionic chip with 64-bit architecture.

Key Features:

  • 4.7-inch (diagonal) widescreen LCD Multi‑Touch display with IPS technology
  • 1334x750-pixel resolution at 326 ppi
  • 1400:1 contrast ratio (typical)
  • 625 cd/m² max brightness (typical)
  • Dual-domain pixels for wide viewing angles
  • Fingerprint-resistant oleophobic coating
